+2. [P1] Fix 2 — `requestStates` is still the old flat model and cannot support ticket rows/reminders — `pages/PublicMenu/x.jsx:1663-1693` documents and uses only `{ status, sentAt, message }`, `pages/PublicMenu/x.jsx:4064` stores `other` as a single object, and `pages/PublicMenu/x.jsx:1700-1704` only formats “just now / X min ago”. The required fields `lastReminderAt`, `reminderCount`, and `remindCooldownUntil` do not exist, and `other` cannot hold multiple concurrent tickets. FIX: expand the standard-type state shape to the new ticket model, store `other` as an array of ticket objects, and update the timer formatter to derive both wait time and reminder metadata from `sentAt` and `lastReminderAt`.
+3. [P1] Fix 3 — repeated taps still open the action modal instead of redirecting to a ticket row — `pages/PublicMenu/x.jsx:3941` sends pending cards to `setCardActionModal(card.id)`, and `pages/PublicMenu/x.jsx:4080-4129` renders the modal with remind/resolve actions. There is no help-board section ref, no per-ticket ref, no `scrollIntoView`, no temporary amber highlight, and no “Запрос уже отправлен — смотри выше” toast path. FIX: delete the modal flow and, in `handleCardTap`, redirect any non-idle request to the `Мои запросы` row via refs, flash that row for 1.5s, and show the bottom toast.
+4. [P1] Fix 4 — reminder flow has no dedicated anti-spam cooldown or countdown state — there is no `handleRemind` function in `x.jsx`, no `remindCooldownUntil` field in `requestStates`, and the only remind path is the old resend UX (`pages/PublicMenu/x.jsx:3959`, `pages/PublicMenu/x.jsx:3995`, `pages/PublicMenu/x.jsx:4100-4104`) that reuses `handleCardTap`. That means no 40s cooldown, no disabled “Повторить через MM:SS” button, and no `reminderCount` tracking. FIX: add `handleRemind(type)` that updates `lastReminderAt`, `reminderCount`, and `remindCooldownUntil`, send the reminder without the undo flow, and bind the row button text/disabled state to the shared timer tick.
+5. [P2] Fix 5 — the required anxiety-reducing copy is missing — there is no `Статус обновляется автоматически` text anywhere in the Help Drawer section, and the old summary block remains instead at `pages/PublicMenu/x.jsx:3916-3926`. FIX: under the new `Мои запросы` section, render the centered helper copy only when at least one active request exists.
+6. [P2] Fix 6 — ticket rows are neither sorted oldest-first nor collapsible at the 4+ threshold — `pages/PublicMenu/x.jsx:1712-1716` builds `pendingRequests` with a raw `Object.entries(...).filter(...)` and no `.sort((a, b) => a.sentAt - b.sentAt)`, and there is no collapse state or “Ещё N запросов” UI in the drawer render at `pages/PublicMenu/x.jsx:3916-4007`. FIX: sort ticket rows by ascending `sentAt`, show all rows for 1-3 active requests, and add the 4+ collapse behavior that keeps only the first two rows visible until expanded.
+7. [P3] Fix 7 — Free-plan gate is blocked by missing `partner.plan` usage in this file — `handleCardTap` at `pages/PublicMenu/x.jsx:1763-1779` starts directly with the undo/send flow, and `x.jsx` contains no `partner?.plan` or `partner.plan` reference at all. Per the task rule, this fix should be skipped if the field is not present in current code; in the current file, it is not present. FIX: confirm that PublicMenu receives a plan field on `partner`; if it does, add the early-return toast gate at the top of `handleCardTap`, otherwise drop Fix 7 from the implementation scope.
+
+## Summary
+Total: 7 findings (0 P0, 4 P1, 2 P2, 1 P3)
+
